lhasa: lhasa (Free Software LHA implementation)
lhasa:
lhasa: Lhasa is a Free Software replacement for the Unix LHA tool, for
lhasa: decompressing .lzh (LHA / LHarc) and .lzs (LArc) archives.
lhasa: The backend for the tool is a library, so that it can be reused
lhasa: for other purposes.
